    "Finally, a three-branch detection head is designed for training and testing.",
    "As shown in Fig. 38, the entire model consists of three separate designs.",
    "The first is the boundary concern module for feature extraction, followed by the transformer decoder in the middle for querying and parallel decoding, and on the far right is a slack matcher for training label allocation.",
    "Many experiments have proven the effectiveness of RTD-Net.",
    "In addition, due to its simple design, RTD-Net is more efficient than the previous two design methods, eliminating the need for non-maximum suppression processing."
